    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've got to see this absolute gem. I\u2019ve honestly babied this car since day one\u2014it\u2019s in stunning, like-new condition and drives like a total dream. Spotless inside and out, it\u2019s practically spent its whole life in a climate-controlled garage. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
