    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've honestly got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and it's in such incredible shape that it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! Not a single scratch or smudge to be found, and it drives as smooth as silk. If you're looking for that 'brand new' feeling without the dealership headache, this is definitely the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive\u2014I promise you're going to love it! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
