      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is an impeccable specimen of BMW\u2019s S54-powered masterpiece. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six delivers linear power through six individual throttle bodies, with the dual-VANOS system recently overhauled for peak timing precision. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission engages with mechanical tactile feedback, paired with a subframe that has been proactively reinforced to maintain structural integrity. This example boasts a pristine chassis with zero oxidation and factory-spec bushings throughout. Inside, the Nappa leather remains supple, and the cockpit is free of any pixel degradation or tactile wear. A true turn-key collector\u2019s piece for the discerning purist.",
